### EventKit API Test Suite
### Use REST Client extension to send requests

@host = http://localhost:8010
@botHost = http://localhost:3978

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health HTTP/1.1

### Recommend (Basic)
GET {{host}}/recommend?interests=ai,agents&top=3 HTTP/1.1

### Recommend (Detailed)
GET {{host}}/recommend?interests=ai,agents,production&top=5&min_score=0.3 HTTP/1.1

### Recommend with Graph (requires auth)
# @name recommendGraph
GET {{host}}/recommend-graph?user_id=user@tenant.com&interests=ai&top=3 HTTP/1.1

### Explain Session
GET {{host}}/explain?session_id=session-1&interests=ai,agents HTTP/1.1

### Export Itinerary
POST {{host}}/export HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "interests": ["ai", "agents", "production"]
  },
  "format": "markdown"
}

### Bot Health Check
GET {{botHost}}/api/health HTTP/1.1

### Get Sessions (Bot API)
GET {{botHost}}/api/sessions HTTP/1.1

### Bot Recommend
POST {{botHost}}/api/recommend HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interests": ["ai", "agents"],
  "top": 3
}

### Telemetry Stats
GET {{host}}/stats HTTP/1.1

### Prometheus Metrics (if enabled)
GET {{host}}/metrics HTTP/1.1

###
### Microsoft Graph API Examples
###

@graphEndpoint = https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get User Profile
GET {{graphEndpoint}}/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get User Events
GET {{graphEndpoint}}/me/events?$select=subject,start,end&$top=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Calendar View
GET {{graphEndpoint}}/me/calendarView?startDateTime=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDateTime=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

